title: Hour 2: Cowboys Concerns
description:
Stephen A., Marcus Spears and Winston Salem St. head football coach Robert Massey and QB Domonique Graves discuss the talent of HBCU programs, what Tua Tagovailoa's captaincy means and why people doubt the Cowboys.
